HEADWORD: Intercommune
<hw>In`ter*com*mune"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Intercommuned</conjf>
<pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Intercommuning</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[Cf. <er>Intercommon</er>,
