[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To intercommunicate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To have mutual communication or intercourse by
conversation.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intercommunicable</ent>⟦br⟧
